928,IssuesEvent,2016-11-21 03:03:22+00:00,42436808,sanand0/xmljson,63734,sanand0,,,closed,XML namespaces,[],[],4,"Hi.

Does this module actually have namespaces support?

For example i have such XML file with custom namespace prefix v8msg:

``` xml
<?xml version=""1.0"" encoding=""UTF-8""?>
<v8msg:Message xmlns:v8msg=""http://v8.1c.ru/messages"">
  <v8msg:Header>
