      <Ref>ec986086-5ba8-11e4-ae81-74f06d6aab21</Ref>
      <DeletionMark>false</DeletionMark>
      <Code>000000001</Code>
      <Description>Роздріб</Description>
    </CatalogObject.ТипыЦенНоменклатуры>
  </v8msg:Body>
</v8msg:Message>
```

After conversion XML - to - JSON and backwards i get this:

``` xml
