I am running the command below to create the python distribution.

```# download and extract Python (using 2.7.12 here as an example)
export PYTHON_ROOT=~/Python
curl -O https://www.python.org/ftp/python/2.7.12/Python-2.7.12.tgz
tar -xvf Python-2.7.12.tgz
rm Python-2.7.12.tgz

# compile into local PYTHON_ROOT
