4765,IssuesEvent,2015-03-17 08:47:58+00:00,2665618,inveniosoftware/invenio,634680,blixhavn,1157480,inveniosoftware,opened,records: 500 error when record does not exist,[],[],0,"When trying to access a rec_ID that does not exist, one should get a pretty 404 message instead of a 500 error. This is probably due to [`guess_primary_collection_of_a_record`](https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio/blob/master/invenio/modules/records/views.py#L66) being called before checking whether the [`record_exists`](https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio/blob/master/invenio/modules/records/views.py#L91).",{},{}
