6558,IssuesEvent,2017-10-17 11:06:13+00:00,25027539,Clinical-Genomics/scout,405278,moonso,6412433,Clinical-Genomics,closed,Always load all variants for MT as default,"[{'id': 136471908, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/Clinical-Genomics/scout/labels/enhancement', 'name': 'enhancement', 'color': '84b6eb', 'default': True}, {'id': 718730511, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/Clinical-Genomics/scout/labels/In%20Project', 'name': 'In Project', 'color': 'c2e0c6', 'default': False}, {'id': 270430031, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/Clinical-Genomics/scout/labels/Intermediate', 'name': 'Intermediate', 'color': 'fbca04', 'default': False}, {'id': 208154656, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/Clinical-Genomics/scout/labels/Qustomer%20Request', 'name': 'Qustomer Request', 'color': 'bfe5bf', 'default': False}, {'id': 618312510, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/Clinical-Genomics/scout/labels/v3.6', 'name': 'v3.6', 'color': 'bfd4f2', 'default': False}]","[{'login': 'moonso', 'id': 405278, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/405278?v=4', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/moonso', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/moonso', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/moonso/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/moonso/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/moonso/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/moonso/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/moonso/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/moonso/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/moonso/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/moonso/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/moonso/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",0,"1000G file: all_wgs_-phase3_v5b.2013-05-02, do not contain MT frequencies and hence MT variants are not filtered from the analysis even if they are common. But they are lowered on frequency in the rank score modell using Mitomap frequencies. 

From a clinical perspective it is desirable to always load all MT variants into Scout i.e. disregard the deafult rank score cut-off when loading. From a WGS MT variant are usually less than 50, so this will not burden the database. ",{},{}
