6763,IssuesEvent,2018-03-06 23:52:59+00:00,25611422,openaddresses/machine,117278,andrewharvey,6895392,openaddresses,opened,sample should respect the layer specified,[],[],0,"I'm not sure what the sample.json is supposed to be but it seems to be a sample of the source data? (it would be handy to get a sample of the output too)

