8673,IssuesEvent,2018-03-06 01:48:02+00:00,26516210,certbot/certbot,220205,jsha,17889013,certbot,opened,route53: Bring back parallel waiting for propagation,[],[],0,"The route53 plugin used to be able to send several update requests, and wait on them all in parallel. It looks like we lost that ability in https://github.com/certbot/certbot/pull/4771, possibly due to a bad rebase. We should bring back that capability. Waiting for the server to declare that it's finished propagating is very slow, and so parallelizing that waiting speeds things up a *lot*.",{},{}
