8860,IssuesEvent,2017-05-07 14:05:54+00:00,37137879,QCoDeS/Qcodes,2694199,giulioungaretti,20478252,QCoDeS,closed, No enqueue from pull #154 ,"[{'id': 222346531, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/QCoDeS/Qcodes/labels/enhancement', 'name': 'enhancement', 'color': 'fbca04', 'default': True}]",[],11,"The joining of the measurements in pull #154 breaks at least two things:
- The notebook becomes unresponsive as it is waiting for the previous loop to finish
- The live plotting stops

