  File ""/Users/crankshaw/miniconda2/envs/pong-rl/lib/python2.7/site-packages/ray/rllib/policy_gradient/policy_gradient.py"", line 258, in compute_action
    return self.model.common_policy.compute_actions(
AttributeError: 'ProximalPolicyLoss' object has no attribute 'compute_actions'
```

cc @robertnishihara: This broke the pong exercise we're putting together.",{},{}
